WIN A £250 VOUCHER EVERY HOUR ✨

Fancy being treated? We're gifting a new follower to a £250 voucher to spend on new summer pieces EVERY HOUR until 6pm 🌴 WANT TO WIN? HERE'S HOW:

1. Make sure you’re following @boohoo
2. ‘LIKE’ this post
3. COMMENT the ‘💸’ emoji below
4. A new prize will be up for grabs EVERY HOUR until 5pm, so come back to this post and comment as many as times as you can each hour for the chance to WIN!

📲 Bonus entry: share this post to your story.

T&C's apply: bit.ly/3CJhcl5. GOOD LUCK!
